Per [Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG)|http://www.w3.org/WAI/intro/wcag], we could implement a checkbox that allows users the option for more time before their session times out when editing page content (["technique" page|http://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG-TECHS/G133.html]).

