When editing wiki pages I frequently use macros which require me to open the Insert drop down and select Other Macros and then search.  For macros I regularly use like Code Block this can be annoying and repetitive.

It would be great if I could specify a macro as a favourite and have it always appear in my Insert drop down.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *Confluence Server*. Using *Confluence Cloud*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFCLOUD-27270].
