I have tried creating a user account in Confluence so that I can file a bug about Intellij 12 EAP patch update process, but there is a bug in Confluence that prohibits me from even making an account, and thus I need to file a bug on it first before I can get to my original issue.  Annoying.

When I try to create an account, there is a CAPTCHA that, no matter how many times I enter it correctly, continuously says that I entered the letters incorrectly and refuses to let me make an account.  Your CAPTCHA system is broken.

