A customer mentioned that sometimes he does not receive page shares in Workbox, only in email notifications.

The potential reason for this could be people entering a full email address rather than searching for and selecting their user in the Share dialog.

If we checked whether the email addresses entered matched with an existing user (either by having email addresses work for searching for a user and selecting them in the Share dialog, or afterwards when sending) we could make sure this method also resulted in the notification going to Workbox

