It took me ages to figure out that I needed to add people to my personal space permissions via the space admin before they could edit my personal pages.

In the attached screenshots, you can see my confusion over why Jurgen could not edit my page.  A simple link to the space admin might help here, or maybe even allowing you to add permissions directly from this dialog.

