WorkBox receives notifications form all UAL'd (linked) JIRA applications.

An admin can disable this at a global level. This issue is to track end-user demand if an end-user wants to disable it only for some JIRA instances and not others.

So in summary, the ability to select which apps can send workbox notifications at a user level.

